                "category": "summary",
                "text": "NVIDIA has released a software update for NVIDIA\u00ae Data Center GPU Manager (DCGM). The update addresses security issues that may lead to denial of service and data tampering. To protect your system, <a href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/dcgm#Downloads\">download and install the latest DCGM release from the CUDA repositories</a>.",
